column1: IF ccr_s_at_d is MF 0 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF  THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_sa_thf_d is MF 2 AND ccr_thb_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_thaldo_d is MF 2 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 1 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_llb_oh_andro_d is MF 0 AND ccr_the_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
